pay!To apply, please submit your cover letter and resume by June 21, 2024 at 4:00 p.m. to jobs@wpl.ca Compensation Starts at $68,213 annually Closes: 21 June, 2024 Waterloo Public Library Waterloo , ON Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
