on $34.97 per hour with a 5% increase in March 2025. Closes: 21 June, 2024 Trail &amp; District Public Library Trail , BC Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
